title: Dirty Heads Home Phantoms of Summer The Acoustic Sessions 2013
description:
The Dirty Heads is a reggae band from Huntington Beach, CA with a melodic style that includes hip hop and ska punk genres. Their debut album, Any Port in a Storm, was released on September 23, 2008, by Executive Music Group. Wikipedia
 Active from: 1996
 Albums: Cabin By the Sea, Any Port in a Storm, Dirty Demos
 Members: Jared Watson, Dustin Bushnell, Jon Olazabal, Matt Ochoa, David Foral
